title: DAZ3D - Boaris for G3M
description:
BOARIS for G3M
--------------
 
https://cdn.pximg.xyz/3be621a648b0ccca67efa7fa69b01f46.jpg

www.daz3d.com/catalog/product/view/id/29281

Big Boaris is one burly bruiser. Leaving the farm he said he could no longer live in the straw and the wood, and made a life for himself in the city of bricks and stone. Now he is no longer troubled by wolves, but the foxes sure love his bacon bits. The set comes complete with custom crafted High Definition Morphs, and a highly detailed texture set, suitable for Iray and 3Delight
